		<td width="150" align="left" valign="top" class="row2"><span class="name"><a name="154767"></a><b>Flunkie</b></span><br /><span class="postdetails">My Job Has No Purpose<br /><br /><br />Joined: 10 Jan 2003<br />Posts: 234<br /></span><br /></td>
		<td class="row2" width="100%" height="28" valign="top"><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
			<tr>
				<td width="100%"><a href="viewtopic.php?p=154767&amp;sid=6e3c3a7fcfaa7a305511d8ce706ff550#154767"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails">Posted: Mon Oct 04, 2004 4:10 pm<span class="gen">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: Performance and Pain</span></td>
				<td valign="top" nowrap="nowrap"><a href="posting.php?mode=quote&amp;p=154767&amp;sid=6e3c3a7fcfaa7a305511d8ce706ff550"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/lang_english/icon_quote.gif" alt="Reply with quote" title="Reply with quote" border="0" /></a>   </td>
